  promptPart1: 'Can you give me balanced stats for a MOBA style video game with a
    specified JSON format? Your result will be used to parse into a JSON format,
    so make sure the entire response is only the JSON, nothing else.



    Use the
    given data in MatchData and EntityData (from a match that actually played out)
    to balance the game as you see fit and output as a new EntityData. Do not change
    any of the named fields of EntityData, only their values.



    MatchData (from
    a real game):'
  promptPart2: 'The Current EntityData from that game: '
  response: 
  testPrompt: can you give me balanced stats for a minion in a MOBA game? it should
    be in the form of the following, and include only the stats, no other text. also,
    please do not use the baseline numbers and only give the two stats listed. [baseHitPoints,
    100],[baseAttackPower, 40] include the comma between brackets in output. for
    reference, the baseline for hp is 100 and baseline for attackpower is 40
